rating_comment: Good economical stay. Cold ac and hot shower water. Nice place with friendly staff and good food. I would stay here again.

I have been a regular visitor at the property but this time it left much to be desired. The booking via Airbnb is only available for the standard rooms that are too small for 2 or more persons. I had stated we would be 2 persons traveling and was disappointed on being given a dingy room. I ended up paying a couple hundreds more to upgrade to their premium room. The behavior of the front desk also wasn't the most cordial. We found a strand of hair in the morning breakfast of puri bhaji. The room was in need of dusting and the washroom needed refills of shower gel. please improve the deficiencies and I might consider opting for this place again.

Rooms are exactly as in pictures.. closeby to NJP station, staff is very courteous. Inhouse 'The Loft' hotel provides delicious meals. The room is sanitised and provides the essentials on check-in. Had a good stay. Thank you.
it's very nice place.
Good place for the cost, friendly staff

Location is really good, in a small alley just next to sevoke road. hence, you stay away from all the noise. Food can be avoided, just about ok at best. lot of scope to improve the cleanliness of the rooms.
All was great
You will enjoy your stay here.

The wifi connectivity within the room was poor, even mobile connectivity inside the room dropped badly. the service was delayed and the intercom facility didn't work on the first day but was rectified on the second day.
This places is tucked in an alley right in the heart of Sevoke Road, opposite to Punjabi Kadhai. It's a nice place for a layover.
well maintained ... recommended

The room in the picture is not the correct room. Very dirty room. They changed my room to a larger but this was also dirty. Contraction going on in the morning. No toilet paper towel or soap was provided I had to ask for everything. The worst place I had stayed on airbnb. This airbnb account is not a part of the hotel but collaborating with the hotel.
